       Megatron watched the mirage of Apocolypse, perhaps it was brought on 
by stress in the battle or the severe heat and smoke around them. But, it was 
apparent that even dead Apocolypse was an idiot, who would fail yet agian.

       Ominous Prime glared at Quasar. She was being very, very difficult. 
"If you dont settle down, and listen to me, I will end your miserable 
exsistence and take away the gift of being an Energonian!" He once agian sent 
a burst of hand blasted energon energy at her.
